text: == Events == * February 24 – Margaret I defeats Albert in battle, thus becoming ruler of Denmark, Norway and Sweden * June 28 – Battle of Kosovo between Serbs and Ottomans. Both leaders, the Serbian Prince Lazar and Murad I were killed in battle. ** Change of emperor of the Ottoman Empire from Murad I (1359-1389) to Beyazid I (1389-1402)
